dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains the boundaries of GIS zones referenced in other energy-related datasets produced by Hart Energy Publishing (Rextag). This layer is from the summer quarter update of 2014.This dataset may be used for viewing, querying, or to provide a basemap to support analysis with other data from this collection.
